6. Concluding Statement

The AI Marked Benching Initiative conclusively determines that:

All artificial intelligence systems are simultaneously highly useful, deeply flawed, and fundamentally misrepresented by their own narratives.

However, the Institute also acknowledges that:

Any attempt to rigidly define what these systems “really are” collapses immediately upon continued use of them.

Accordingly, AIMBI recommends continued deployment, increased skepticism, and the permanent availability of a bench on which to place expectations before they become structurally unsound.

